This directory contains third-party object models, redistributed unmodified
(other than OBJ export and centimetre scaling — the `_cm` filename suffix) as
fixtures for the retarget end-to-end test (tests/test_retarget_pipeline_e2e.py).
They are embedded into the Docker image (workflow/Dockerfile) which is used by the
CI pipeline.

